(6, 2, 91, 5, 'Savings Muamalat iB Hajj and Umrah', '<p><strong><span class=\"short_text\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\"><img src=\"http://muamalat.manifesto.co.id/assets/backend/js/tinymce/plugins/image/uploads/3._Tabungan_Haji_dan_Umrah_iB.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"375\" /></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><span id=\"result_box\" class=\"short_text\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\">Why</span> <span class=\"hps\">Hajj</span> <span class=\"hps\">and</span> <span class=\"hps\">Umrah</span> <span class=\"hps\">with Bank</span> <span class=\"hps\">Muamalat</span>?</span></strong><br /><br /><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\">As the</span> <span class=\"hps\">first</span> <span class=\"hps\">Islamic commercial</span> <span class=\"hps\">bank</span> <span class=\"hps\">in</span> <span class=\"hps\">Indonesia</span>, <span class=\"hps\">Bank</span> <span class=\"hps\">Muamalat</span> <span class=\"hps\">since 1999</span> <span class=\"hps\">always</span> <span class=\"hps\">gained the confidence</span> <span class=\"hps\">of the</span> <span class=\"hps\">Ministry of Religious Affairs</span> <span class=\"hps\">to be one of</span> <span class=\"hps\">BPS</span> <span class=\"hps\">BPIH</span> <span class=\"hps atn\">(</span>Beneficiary <span class=\"hps\">Bank</span><span class=\"hps\">Deposit</span> <span class=\"hps\">Cost</span> <span class=\"hps\">Hajj</span>). <span class=\"hps\">Therefore</span>, <span class=\"hps\">the professionalism of</span> <span class=\"hps\">Bank</span> <span class=\"hps\">Muamalat</span> <span class=\"hps\">in</span> <span class=\"hps\">delivering</span> <span class=\"hps\">their customers</span> <span class=\"hps\">to be able to</span> <span class=\"hps\">leave</span> <span class=\"hps\">hajj</span> <span class=\"hps\">and</span> <span class=\"hps\">umrah</span> <span class=\"hps\">certainly</span> <span class=\"hps\">can not be doubted</span></span><span lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"-1\"><span title=\"Karenanya, profesionalitas Bank Muamalat dalam mengantarkan nasabah-nasabahnya untuk bisa berangkat beribadah haji tentu tak perlu diragukan lagi.\r\n\r\n\">.</span></span></p>', '<p class=\"teks\"><strong><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"-1\"><span title=\"Praktis\r\n\r\n\">Practical</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"teks\"><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\">You and your family</span> <span class=\"hps\">do not</span> <span class=\"hps\">need to carry</span> <span class=\"hps\">excessive</span> <span class=\"hps\">cash</span>. <span class=\"hps\">As the owner of Savings</span></span><span lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\">Muamalat</span> iB&nbsp;<span class=\"hps\">Hajj</span> <span class=\"hps\">and</span> <span class=\"hps\">Umrah</span>, <span class=\"hps\">you</span> <span class=\"hps\">will receive</span> <span class=\"hps\">a card</span> <span class=\"hps\">Shar</span><span class=\"atn\">-</span>E <span class=\"hps\">Gold</span> <span class=\"hps\">*</span> <span class=\"hps\">that you can use</span> <span class=\"hps\">to transact</span> <span class=\"hps\">in all</span> <span class=\"hps\">places</span> <span class=\"hps\">that accept</span> <span class=\"hps\">VISA</span> <span class=\"hps\">cards</span>.</span></p>\r\n<div><strong><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"-1\"><span title=\"Menenangkan\r\n\r\n\">Soothe</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<p class=\"teks\"><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"-1\"><span title=\"Dana nasabah dikelola secara syariah sehingga memberi ketenangan batin dalam menjalankan ibadah haji di tanah suci.\r\n\">Customer funds managed by sharia so as to give peace of mind in performing pilgrimage in the holy land.</span></span></p>\r\n<div><strong><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"-1\"><span title=\"Fleksibel\r\n\r\n\">Flexible</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<p class=\"teks\"><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"-1\"><span title=\"Anda dapat memilih jangka waktu dan jumlah setoran, sesuai paket yang tersedia.\r\n\">You can select the length of time and amount of deposit, according to the package are available.</span></span></p>\r\n<div><strong><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"-1\"><span title=\"Menguntungkan\r\n\r\n\">Profitable</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<p class=\"teks\"><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"-1\"><span title=\"Dimungkinkan memperoleh bonus serta souvenir haji **.\r\n\">It is possible to obtain bonuses and pilgrim souvenirs **.</span></span></p>\r\n<div><strong><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"-1\"><span title=\"Terjamin\r\n\r\n\">Guaranteed</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<p class=\"teks\"><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"-1\"><span title=\"Bank online dengan SISKOHAT Kementrian Agama untuk memperoleh kepastian mendapatkan kuota / porsi keberangkatan ibadah haji.\r\n\r\n\">Bank online with SISKOHAT Ministry of Religious Affairs to obtain assurance get quota / departure portion of the pilgrimage.</span></span><br />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"teks\"><em>* <span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\">Savings</span> <span class=\"hps\">Muamalat iB</span> <span class=\"hps\">Hajj</span> <span class=\"hps\">and</span> <span class=\"hps\">Umrah</span> <span class=\"hps\">are</span> <span class=\"hps\">using</span> <span class=\"hps\">facilitation</span> <span class=\"hps\">SI</span> <span class=\"hps atn\">(</span>Standing <span class=\"hps\">Instruction)</span> <span class=\"hps\">of</span> <span class=\"hps\">the Regular</span> <span class=\"hps\">Savings</span>.</span></em></p>\r\n<p class=\"teks\"><em>**<span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"-1\"><span title=\"** Souvenir tergantung kebijakan Bank Muamalat\r\n\r\n\">Souvenir depending on the policy of Bank Muamalat</span></span></em></p>', '<p>Photocopy of identity card (KTP / SIM for citizen and KIMS / Permits and Passports for foreigners/Letters of reference) and fill Opening Form.</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"height: 437px;\" border=\"1\" width=\"519\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<td width=\"180\"><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"-1\"><span title=\"Jenis Rekening	dapat dibuka secara perorangan dan QQ dengan pihak yang diwakili / mewakili\r\n\">Type of Account</span></span></td>\r\n<td width=\"320\"><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\">Individual account</span> <span class=\"hps\">and</span> <span class=\"hps\">can be</span> <span class=\"hps\">reserved</span> <span class=\"hps\">on behalf of</span> <span class=\"hps\">children (under</span> <span class=\"hps\">17 years</span>) <span class=\"hps\">and is available</span> <span class=\"hps\">in a choice of</span> <span class=\"hps\">currencies</span> <span class=\"hps\">IDR</span><span class=\"hps\">or</span> <span class=\"hps\">USD</span></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"even\">\r\n<td><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"-1\"><span title=\"perjanjian	Wadiah\r\n\">Agreement</span></span></td>\r\n<td>Wadiah</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<td><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"-1\"><span title=\"Setoran Awal Minimum	Rp 100.000\r\n\">Minimum Initial Deposit</span></span></td>\r\n<td>Rp 50.000,- / USD 20,-</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"even\">\r\n<td><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"-1\"><span title=\"Saldo Minimum	Rp 100.000\r\n\">Minimum Balanc</span></span></td>\r\n<td>Rp 50.000,- / USD 5,-</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<td><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"-1\"><span title=\"Biaya\r\n\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\">Charge</span></span></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\">Free</span> <span class=\"hps\">administration</span></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\">Replacement</span> <span class=\"hps\">Passbook</span> <span class=\"hps\">Rp 10.000</span