(42, 2, 91, 41, 'Muamalat Saving Umrah iB', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span class=\"hps\"><img src=\"http://muamalat.manifesto.co.id/assets/backend/js/tinymce/plugins/image/uploads/4._Mumalat_Umrah_iB.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"375\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span class=\"hps\">Whenever</span> <span class=\"hps\">you</span> <span class=\"hps\">want</span> <span class=\"hps\">to go umrah</span>, <span class=\"hps\">Muamalat Saving</span> Umrah <span class=\"hps\">iB</span> <span class=\"hps\">will</span> <span class=\"hps\">help</span> <span class=\"hps\">you</span> <span class=\"hps\">plan</span> <span class=\"hps\">easily</span>.</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span id=\"result_box\" class=\"short_text\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\">Deposit</span> <span class=\"hps\">Lightweight</span> <span class=\"hps\">and</span> <span class=\"hps\">Affordable</span></span>.</strong></span></p>\r\n<div><span id=\"result_box\" class=\"short_text\" lang=\"en\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span class=\"hps\">Monthly deposit</span> <span class=\"hps\">accounts</span> <span class=\"hps\">ranging</span> <span class=\"hps\">from</span> <span class=\"hps\">Rp</span> <span class=\"hps\">100,000</span></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Fleksibel</strong></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">- <span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\">Designed specifically</span> <span class=\"hps\">to</span> <span class=\"hps\">address the needs of</span> <span class=\"hps\">Umrah</span> <span class=\"hps\">worship</span> <span class=\"hps\">planning</span>.</span></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">- <span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\">Option</span> <span class=\"hps\">Investment Period</span> <span class=\"hps\">3</span> <span class=\"hps\">months</span> <span class=\"hps\">to 5 years</span> <span class=\"hps\">tailored to</span> <span class=\"hps\">customers\' needs</span>.</span></span><br /><span id=\"result_box\" class=\"short_text\" lang=\"en\"></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span id=\"result_box\" class=\"short_text\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\">Measured</span></span></strong></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Providing simulation monthly deposit required in order to achieve the funding requirements for worship Umrah.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Cozy</strong></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">- Management of sharia funds provide a sense of comfort and confidence for the future.</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">- Customers enjoy free autodebit that automatically transfer funds monthly deposits of account funding sources.</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">- Balance Savings iB Muamalat Umrah automatically transferred to the account of the source of funds as they mature.</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Profitable</strong></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">- Customers enjoy the competitive results so that the Customer deposits grew optimally.</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">- Free monthly administration fee.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Protect</strong></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">- Customers get life insurance cover * for free without the need for a medical check-up, the charges incurred by the Bank Muamalat.</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">- The value of the insured up to Rp 1 billion (one billion dollars) per customer with the following conditions:</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">a. To save time &le; 6 months :</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">The insurance company will pay the remaining monthly payments that have not been done in lumsump customers plus mourning facility 20 times the monthly payment if the Customer dies due to an accident.</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">b. To save time&gt; 6 months to 20 years :</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">The insurance company will pay the remaining monthly payments that have not been done in lumsump customers plus mourning facility 20 times the monthly payment if the Customer dies due to an accident or died of natural..</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Illustration:</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Customer A wants to prepare for the Umrah worship fund of Rp 25 million to open a Muamalat Saving Umrah iB</span></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Save selected time period for 60 months (5 years)</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Prepared monthly payment is Rp 400.000 per month</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">On the way to save for 24 months, a customer experience that results in something dies, the funds received by the heirs are as follows :</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">- The rest of the regular deposit insurance paid = Rp 400.000 x 36 = Rp 14.400.000</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">- Compensation grief for heirs = 20 x Rp 400.000 = Rp 8.000.000</span></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Total funds received by heirs according planned by the previous customer = Rp14.400.000 + Rp 8.000.000 = Rp 22.400.000</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><em>*) Savings iB Muamalat Umrah equipped with life insurance sharia Islamic insurance company in collaboration with the Bank. Approval of claims following the terms and conditions of the insurance company.</em></span></div>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\">Age at</span> <span class=\"hps\">least 17 years</span> <span class=\"hps\">of account opening</span>, <span class=\"hps\">a maximum of</span> <span class=\"hps\">60 years</span></span>.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\">Age at time of</span> <span class=\"hps\">Muamalat</span> Saving Umrah iB <span class=\"hps\">Plan</span> <span class=\"hps\">maximum</span><span class=\"hps\">maturity of</span> <span class=\"hps\">65</span> <span class=\"hps\">years</span></span>.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\">Savings</span> <span class=\"hps\">accounts</span> <span class=\"hps\">iB</span> <span class=\"hps\">Muamalat</span> <span class=\"hps\">as</span> <span class=\"hps\">a source of</span> <span class=\"hps\">funds</span> <span class=\"hps\">accounts</span></span>.</span></li>\r\n</ol>', '<table class=\"teks\" border=\"1\" width=\"548\" cellpadding=\"5\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<td bgcolor=\"#E3D0F2\">\r\n<div>Akad</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td bgcolor=\"#E3D0F2\">\r\n<div>Mudharabah Mutlaqah</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"even\">\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Nisbah</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>30%</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<td bgcolor=\"#E3D0F2\">\r\n<div><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\">Monthly</span> <span class=\"hps\">deposit</span></span></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td bgcolor=\"#E3D0F2\">\r\n<div>Starting From Rp 100.000</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"even\">\r\n<td>\r\n<div><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\">Term</span> <span class=\"hps\">Savings</span></span></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hps\">3