(70, 2, 115, 69, 'Dollar savings Transactions', '<p class=\"teks\"><img src=\"http://muamalat.manifesto.co.id/assets/backend/js/tinymce/plugins/image/uploads/2._Tabungan_Mamalat_Dollar.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"375\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"teks\">Islamic savings in foreign exchange denominated U.S. Dollar (USD) and Singapore Dollar (SGD) are intended to serve the needs of investment transactions and more diverse, especially those involving currency USD and SGD</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>Assign :</h4>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"teks\">Individuals 18 years of age and who have legality body Institutions</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>Featured Feature :</h4>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol class=\"teks\">\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Free administration fees for Savings Transactions USD with an average balance of&gt; USD 1,000</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Free account closing fee</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Free transfers between bank accounts throughout the network office Muamalat Bank Muamalat</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Can transact in Foreign Exchange Bank Muamalat branch network throughout Indonesia</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Able to transact at Bank Muamalat office network in Malaysia and Batam</li>\r\n</ol>', '<ol class=\"teks\">\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Opportunity to get monthly bonus</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Opportunity to gain foreign investments in the dollar exchange</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Can avoid exchange rate risk on non-payment of duty by way of organizing rupiah liquidity directly in the form of Dollars</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Online around the outlet of Bank Muamalat</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Safe and secure</li>\r\n</ol>', '<ol class=\"teks\">\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><strong>Minimum initial deposit:</strong> USD 100 100/SGD</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><strong>For individuals</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">WNI: KTP / SIM / Passport that is still going/Letter of Statement</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">WNA : KIMS/KITAS/Letter of reference</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><strong>For institutions</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">TIN institutions still occur</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Legality stance and changes (if any)</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">The licenses of business: SIUP, TDP, SKD, and other situ (if needed) are still valid</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Enterprise data management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>', '<ol class=\"teks\">\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Based on the principles of sharia with wadiah contract (titipan)</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Minimum Balance: USD 50 / SGD 50</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Administration fees:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Denominated in USD\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Free (average balances&gt; = USD 1,000)</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">0,5 USD / month (average balance of</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Denominated in SGD\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">SGD 0.5 / month</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Following minimum deposit: USD 50 / SGD 50</li>\r\n</ol>', 'dollar-savings-transactions', 'dollar-savings-transactions', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_590_tabungan_muamalat_dollar.jpg', 'home_list_produk_service_560_2__tabungan_mamalat_dollar.jpg', '', 'list_produk_service_590_tabungan_muamalat_dollar_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 8, 0, 0, '2016-03-01 00:56:37', '2016-03-19 14:40:25', 'admin', 'admin'),
(71, 1, 115, 71, 'Tabungan Muamalat Prima iB', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><img src=\"http://muamalat.manifesto.co.id/assets/backend/js/tinymce/plugins/image/uploads/7._Muamalat_Prima_iB.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"375\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Tabungan Muamalat Prima iB dipersembahkan bagi Anda yang mendambakan hasil maksimal dan kebebasan bertransaksi.</span></p>', '<p class=\"teks\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Lengkap dan Nyaman</strong></span></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"teks\">Dilengkapi dengan Kartu Gold untuk keleluasaan transaksi di SELURUH DUNIA melalui jaringan ATM Bank Muamalat, ATM Prima, ATM Bersama, MEPS, dan ATM PLUS/VISA serta pembayaran belanja di jaringan Visa.</li>\r\n<li class=\"teks\">Kenyamanan bertransaksi kapan saja dan dimana saja melalui layanan <em>electronic banking</em>Bank Muamalat (ATM, <em>Internet Banking</em>, <em>Mobile Banking</em> dan <em>Phone Banking</em>).</li>\r\n<li class=\"teks\">Nasabah dapat menikmati <em>waad</em> nisbah sebagai berikut.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<div><img class=\"pyro-image alignment-none\" src=\"http://bankmuamalat.co.id/files/large/12db578a83fe28d\" alt=\"\" width=\"444\" height=\"151\" data-pyroimage=\"true\" /></div>', '<p class=\"teks\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Nasabah Perorangan</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"teks\">a. Mengisi formulir pembukaan rekening<br />b. Kartu identitas:<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - WNI: KTP / SIM / Paspor yang masih berlaku dan NPWP/Surat pernyataan<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - WNA: KITAS / KIMS/Paspor/Surat referensi<br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Nasabah Non Perorangan</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"teks\">a. Mengisi formulir pembukaan rekening<br />b. Dokumen yang diperlukan:<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - NPWP<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - Akta Pendirian dan Perubahan (jika ada)<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - Izin usaha yaitu TDP dan SIUP bagi badan usaha<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - Surat kuasa penunjukkan pengelolaan rekening<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - Bukti identitas diri penerima dan pemberi kuasa</p>', '<p class=\"teks\"><img class=\"pyro-image alignment-none\" src=\"http://bankmuamalat.co.id/files/large/57d8ffbd6ed1664\" alt=\"\" width=\"1650\" height=\"887\" data-pyroimage=\"true\" /><br />*Rekening aktif adalah rekening nasabah yang aktif melakukan transaksi selain transaksi sistem</p>', 'tabungan-muamalat-prima-ib', 'tabungan-muamalat-prima-ib', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_987_tabungan_muamalat_prima_ib.jpg', 'home_list_produk_service_904_7__muamalat_prima_ib.jpg', '', 'list_produk_service_987_tabungan_muamalat_prima_ib_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 13, 0, 0, '2016-03-01 06:34:37', '2016-03-19 14:55:25', 'admin', 'admin'),
(72, 2, 115, 71, 'Tabungan Muamalat Prima iB', '<p><img src=\"http://muamalat.manifesto.co.id/assets/backend/js/tinymce/plugins/image/uploads/7._Muamalat_Prima_iB.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"375\" /></p>', '', '', '', 'tabungan-muamalat-prima-ib', 'tabungan-muamalat-prima-ib', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_750_tabungan_muamalat_prima_ib.jpg', 'home_list_produk_service_95_7__muamalat_prima_ib.jpg', '', 'list_produk_service_750_tabungan_muamalat_prima_ib_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 13, 0, 0, '2016-03-01 06:34:37', '2016-03-19 14:55:25', 'admin', 'admin'),
(73, 1, 117, 73, 'Giro Muamalat Attijary iB', '<p><img src=\"http://muamalat.manifesto.co.id/assets/backend/js/tinymce/plugins/image/uploads/Giro_Muamalat_Attijary_iB.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"375\" /></p>\r\n<p>Produk giro berbasis akad wadiah yang memberikan kemudahan dan kenyamanan dalam bertransaksi. Merupakan sarana untuk memenuhi kebutuhan transaksi bisnis Nasabah Non-perorangan yang didukung oleh fasilitas Cash Management.</p>', '<ol>\r\n<li>Kemudahan bertransaksi, Produk ini menyediakan fleksibilitas bagi nasabah</li>\r\n<li>Bebas biaya administrasi bulanan selama memenuhi kriteria saldo minimum</li>\r\n<li>Tersedia dalam 4 jenis mata uang: IDR, USD, SGD, EUR</li>\r\n<li>Fasilitas Cash Management System (CMS)</li>\r\n</ol>', '', '<ol>\r\n<li>Setoran Awal: IDR 1.000.000 / USD 100 / SGD 100 / EUR 100</li>\r\n<li>Saldo Minimum: IDR 1.000.000 / USD 100 / SGD 100 / EUR 100</li>\r\n<li>Biaya Administrasi:&nbsp;\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\">\r\n<li>IDR s/d&nbsp;s/d =1.000.000 =&nbsp;Bebas</li>\r\n<li>USD s/d 100 = 1 ; &ge; 100 = Bebas</li>\r\n<li>SGD s/d 100 = 1 ; &ge; 100 = Bebas</li>\r\n<li>EUR s/d 100 = 1 ; &ge; 100 = Bebas</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Biaya penutupan: IDR 50.000 / USD 5 / SGD 5 / EUR 5</li>\r\n<li>Biaya Cek/BG: Rp 100.000 (hanya IDR)</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><em>*Biaya lain-lain dan pajak diatur sesuai dengan ketentuan yang berlaku dalam Daftar Tarif Produk &amp; Layanan Bank</em></p>', 'giro-muamalat-attijary-ib', 'giro-muamalat-attijary-ib', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_375_giro-att.jpg', 'home_list_produk_service_714_giro_muamalat_attijary_ib.jpg', '', 'list_produk_service_375_giro-att_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 16, 0, 0, '2016-03-01 05:10:42', '2016-03-19 15:02:51', 'admin', 'admin'),
(74, 2, 117, 73, 'Muamalat Attijary iB Giro', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Wadiah contract-based giro product&nbsp;which provide ease and convenience in transaction. A means to meet the needs of individual customer business transactions and non-individuals supported by Cash Management facility</span></p>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #333333;\">Easy&nbsp;transaction. This product provides the flexibility for customers</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #333333;\">Free monthly administration fee</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #333333;\">Available in 3 types of currencies: IDR, USD, SGD</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #333333;\">Regular ATM card facilities for individual customers</span></li>\r\n</ol>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Fill out and complete the account opening form.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Submit the original documents and ID / Passport or KIMS / KITAS / KITAP applicable</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Enclose&nbsp;NPWP</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Enclose a&nbsp;reference letter (if required)</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Enclose&nbsp;a letter of authorization (if authorized)</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Copy of Certificate of incorporation and amendments (if any) that have been approved by the Ministry of Justice.&nbsp;<strong>(Non-Individual)</strong></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Copy of proof of identity of the board and show the original files.&nbsp;<strong>(Non-</strong><strong>Individual)</strong></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">SIUP/TDP/SITU.&nbsp;<strong>(Non-</strong><strong>Individual</strong><strong>)</strong></span></li>\r\n</ol>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Initial Deposit: IDR 1.000.000/ USD 100/ SGD 100</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Minimum Balance: IDR 1.000.000/ USD 100/ SGD 100</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Administrative Fee:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">- IDR s/d =1.000.000 = Free</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">- USD s/d 100 = 1; &gt;=100 = Free</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">- SGD s/d 100 = 1; &gt;=100 = Free</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Closing Fee: IDR 50.000/ USD 5/ SGD 5</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">ATM Card Fee: Free</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Cost Cheque/ BG: IDR 100,000 (IDR only)</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">*Other costs and taxes are set in accordance with the applicable provisions of the Listing Products &amp; Services Bank Rates</span></p>', 'muamalat-attijary-ib-giro', 'muamalat-attijary-ib-giro', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_654_giro-att.jpg', 'home_list_produk_service_10_giro_muamalat_attijary_ib.jpg', '', 'list_produk_service_654_giro-att_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 16, 0, 0, '2016-03-01 05:10:42', '2016-03-19 15:02:51', 'admin', 'admin'),
(75, 1, 117, 75, 'Giro Muamalat Ultima iB', '<p><img src=\"http://muamalat.manifesto.co.id/assets/backend/js/tinymce/plugins/image/uploads/Giro_Muamalat_Ultima_iB.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"375\" /></p>\r\n<p>Produk giro berbasis akad mudharabah yang memberikan kemudahan bertransaksi dan bagi hasil yang kompetitif. Sarana bagi nasabah perorangan dan non-perorangan untuk memenuhi kebutuhan transaksi bisnis sekaligus memberikan imbal hasil yang optimal.</p>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Memberikan bagi hasil/profit yang optimal</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Kemudahan pengaturan likuiditas nasabah</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Tersedia dalam 2 jenis mata uang: IDR, USD</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Fasilitas kartu ATM Visa Debit Gold untuk nasabah perorangan</li>\r\n</ol>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Mengisi dan melengkapi formulir pembukaan rekening</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Menyerahkan dan menunjukkan dokumen asli KTP/Paspor atau KIMS/KITAS/KITAP yang berlaku</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Melampirkan NPWP</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Melampirkan surat referensi (bila diperlukan)</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Melampirkan surat kuasa (apabila dikuasakan)</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Fotokopi Akte pendirian dan perubahannya (bila ada) yang telah disahkan oleh Menteri Kehakiman. <strong>(Non-Individu)</strong></li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Fotokopi bukti identitas para pengurus serta menunjukkan berkas-berkas aslinya. <strong>(Non-Individu&gt;</strong></li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">SIUP/TDP/SITU. <strong>(Non-Individu)</strong></li>\r\n</ol>', '<h4>Fitur Produk :</h4>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Setoran Awal : IDR 25.000.000 / USD 2.500</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Saldo Minimum : IDR 25.000.000 / USD 10.000</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Biaya Administrasi :\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">IDR s/d =25.000.000 = Rp 25.000</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">USD s/d =10.000 = USD 2,5</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Biaya Penutupan : IDR Rp 100.000 / USD 10</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Tersedia Cek/Bilyet Giro (untuk IDR)</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Tersedia fasilitas kartu ATM Visa Debit Gold (untuk perorangan)</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Adanya bagi hasil</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>*Biaya-biaya lain dan pajak diatur sesuai dengan ketentuan yang berlaku dalam Daftar Tarif Produk &amp; Layanan Bank</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>Nisbah Bagi Hasil</h4>\r\n<p><br />Mata Uang IDR</p>\r\n<table style=\"height: 254px;\" border=\"1\" width=\"374\" cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<th scope=\"col\">Tiering Saldo</th>\r\n<th scope=\"col\">Nisbah<br />Nasabah</th>\r\n<th scope=\"col\">Wa\'ad<br />Nisbah</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<td>s/d &lt; IDR 25 juta</td>\r\n<td>1</td>\r\n<td>-</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"even\">\r\n<td>IDR 25 Juta s/d &lt; IDR 250 juta</td>\r\n<td>1</td>\r\n<td>19</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<td>IDR 250 Juta s/d &lt; IDR 1 Milyar</td>\r\n<td>1</td>\r\n<td>29</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"even\">\r\n<td>IDR 1 Milyar s/d &lt; IDR 10 Milyar</td>\r\n<td>1</td>\r\n<td>39</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<td>IDR 10 Milyar s/d &lt; 25&nbsp;Milyar</td>\r\n<td>1</td>\r\n<td>46.5</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"even\">\r\n<td>&ge; IDR 25 Milyar</td>\r\n<td>1</td>\r\n<td>49</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br /><br />Mata Uang USD</p>\r\n<table style=\"height: 173px;\" border=\"1\" width=\"374\" cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<th scope=\"col\">Tiering Saldo</th>\r\n<th scope=\"col\">&nbsp;Nisbah<br />&nbsp;Nasabah</th>\r\n<th scope=\"col\">&nbsp; Wa\'ad &nbsp;<br />Nisbah</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"even\">\r\n<td>s/d &lt; USD 2,500</td>\r\n<td>1</td>\r\n<td>-</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<td>USD 2,500 s/d &lt; USD 100,000</td>\r\n<td>1</td>\r\n<td>9</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"even\">\r\n<td>&ge; USD 100,000</td>\r\n<td>1</td>\r\n<td>14</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'giro-muamalat-ultima-ib', 'giro-muamalat-ultima-ib', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_285_giro_muamalat_ultima_ib.jpg', 'home_list_produk_service_783_giro_muamalat_ultima_ib.jpg', '', 'list_produk_service_285_giro_muamalat_ultima_ib_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 17, 0, 0, '2016-03-15 04:20:23', '2016-03-19 15:03:56', 'admin', 'admin'),
(76, 2, 117, 75, 'Muamalat Ultima iB Giro', '<p><img src=\"http://muamalat.manifesto.co.id/assets/backend/js/tinymce/plugins/image/uploads/Giro_Muamalat_Ultima_iB.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"375\" /></p>\r\n<p>Akad&nbsp;mudharabah - based giro product transaction and for competitive results. Means for non-individual customers and to meet the needs of individual business transactions while providing optimal returns.</p>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Provide optimal profit</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Ease liquidity&nbsp;customer arrangements</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Available in 2 types of currency: IDR, USD</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">ATM Visa Debit Gold Card facilities&nbsp;for individual customers</li>\r\n</ol>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Fill out and complete the account opening form</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Submit the original documents and ID / Passport or KIMS / KITAS / KITAP applicable</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Enclose NPWP</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Enclose a reference letter (if required)</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Enclose a letter of authorization (if authorized)</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Copy of certificate of incorporation and amendments (if any) that have been approved by the Ministry of Justice.&nbsp;<strong>(Non-Individual)</strong></li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Copy of proof of identity of the board, and show the original files.&nbsp;<strong>(Non-Individual)</strong></li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Valid SIUP/TDP/SITU.&nbsp;<strong>(Non-Individual)</strong></li>\r\n</ol>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Initial Deposit : IDR 25.000.000 / USD 2.500</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Minimum Balance : IDR 25.000.000 / USD 10.000</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Administrative Fees :\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">IDR s/d =25.000.000 = Rp 25.000</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">USD s/d =10.000 = USD 2,5</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Closing Fees : IDR Rp 100.000 / USD 10</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Available Cheque / Giro (for USD)</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Available Visa Debit&nbsp;Gold ATM card facilities (for individuals)</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Profit Sharing</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>*Other costs and taxes are set in accordance with the applicable provisions of the Listing Products &amp; Services Bank Rates</p>', 'muamalat-ultima-ib-giro', 'muamalat-ultima-ib-giro', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_4_giro_muamalat_ultima_ib.jpg', 'home_list_produk_service_781_giro_muamalat_ultima_ib.jpg', '', 'list_produk_service_4_giro_muamalat_ultima_ib_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 17, 0, 0, '2016-03-15 04:20:23', '2016-03-19 15:03:56', 'admin', 'admin'),
(77, 1, 119, 77, 'Deposito Mudharabah iB Muamalat', '<p><img src=\"http://muamalat.manifesto.co.id/assets/backend/js/tinymce/plugins/image/uploads/Deposito_Mudharabah_iB.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"999\" height=\"375\" /></p>\r\n<p>Deposito syariah dalam mata uang Rupiah dan US Dollar yang fleksibel dan memberikan hasil investasi yang optimal bagi Anda.</p>', '<p><strong>Menguntungkan</strong><br />Memperoleh bagi hasil yang kompetitif setiap bulan<br /><br /><strong>Ketenangan di hati</strong><br />Dana investasi nasabah dikelola secara Syariah, sehingga memberikan ketenangan batin dalam berinvestasi<br /><br /><strong>Fleksibel</strong><br />Tersedia pilihan jangka waktu investasi<br /><br /><strong>Sebagai Jaminan</strong><br />Dapat digunakan sebagi jaminan pembiayaan atau untuk referensi Bank Muamalat.</p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Perorangan</strong></span></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\">\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">WNI</span>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\">\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">KTP/SIM/Paspor yang masih berlaku</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">NPWP atau surat pernyataan terkait kepemilikan NPWP/Surat pernyataan</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">WNA</span>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\">\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">KIMS/KITAS/Surat referensi</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Perusahaan/Institusi</strong></span></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">NPWP</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Dokumen legalisasi</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Dokumen izin usaha</span></li>\r\n</ol>', '<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Deposito Mudharabah</span> </strong><br />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"height: 295px;\" border=\"1\" width=\"461\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<td width=\"180\"><span