(97, 1, 127, 97, 'Layanan Cash Pick-up and Delivery', '<p>Untuk layanan pengantaran ataupun penjemputan uang tunai dan warkat bilyet giro dari dan ke lokasi usaha Anda, kami menyediakan Cash Pick Up and Delivery Services. Layanan ini merupakan solusi kebutuhan Anda terhadap layanan collection terutama yang berasal dari <em>cash</em>.<br /> <br /><strong>Cash Delivery Services</strong></p>\r\n<p>Layanan pengantaran uang tunai dan warkat bilyet giro ke lokasi usaha Anda yang disediakan oleh Bank Muamalat Indonesia.<br /> <br /><strong>Cash Pick Up Services</strong></p>\r\n<p>Layanan penjemputan uang tunai dan warkat bilyet giro dari lokasi usaha Anda yang disediakan Bank Muamalat Indonesia.<br /> <br />Dengan solusi Cash Pick Up and Delivery Services, kebutuhan cash collection Anda dapat terpenuhi melalui sistem:<br />1. <strong>Said to Contain</strong>.&nbsp;Proses pengantaran atau penjemputan uang tunai atau warkat bilyet giro dilakukan secara bundle dan uang yang tidak dapat di-bundle sesuai ketentuan akan dihitung secara rinci oleh pihak vendor.</p>\r\n<p>2. <strong>Count on Site</strong>.&nbsp;Proses pengantaran atau penjemputan uang tunai atau warkat bilyet giro dilakukan dengan cara menghitung uang secara rinci per lembar di lokasi usaha Anda.</p>', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Benefit yang akan Anda rasakan:<br />1. Memberikan keamanan dalam proses setoran uang dalam perjalanan.<br />2. Solusi bagi perusahaan dalam rekonsiliasi hasil penjualan agar berjalan secara cepat, akurat, dan efisien.<br />3. Solusi bagi perusahaan yang menginginkan hasil penjualannya dapat segera dimasukkan ke dalam kas perusahaan yang tersimpan di Bank.<br />4. Solusi bagi perusahaan untuk cash collection dari cabang-cabangnya yang tersebar di berbagai daerah.</p>', '', '', 'layanan-cash-pick-up-and-delivery', 'layanan-cash-pick-up-and-delivery', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_34_depositolay.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_34_depositolay_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 04:34:04', '2016-03-20 07:26:51', 'admin', 'admin'),
(98, 2, 127, 97, 'Cash Pick-up and Delivery Services', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">For cash and giro cheque pick up or delivery services to or from your business location, we provide Cash Pick Up and Delivery Services. This service is Your solution for cash collection.<br /> <br /><strong>Cash Delivery Services</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cash or giro cheque delivery services to Your business location provided by Bank Muamalat Indonesia.<br /> <br /><strong>Cash Pick Up Services</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cash or giro cheque pick up services from Your business location provided by Bank Muamalat Indonesia.<br /> <br />By Cash Pick Up and Delivery Services solution, your cash collection needs can be fulfilled by these systems:</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">1. <strong>Said to Contain</strong>.&nbsp;Cash or giro cheque pick up or delivery process counted in bundle and cash that can&rsquo;t be counted in bundle according to the term, counted detailly by the vendor.<br />2. <strong>Count on Site</strong>.&nbsp;Cash or giro cheque pick up or delivery process done by count it detailly per sheet at Your business location.</p>', '<p>Benefits that You will get:<br />1. Safety in deposit process.<br />3. Fast, accurate, and efficient proceeds reconsiliation .<br />4. Solution for Your corporate that wants your proceeds deposit in corporate account in the Bank immediately.<br />5. Solution for corporates that need cash collection from their branches that spread in many location.</p>', '', '', 'cash-pick-up-and-delivery-services', 'cash-pick-up-and-delivery-services', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_573_depositolay.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_573_depositolay_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 04:34:04', '2016-03-20 07:26:51', 'admin', 'admin'),
(99, 1, 127, 99, 'Jasa Layanan Escrow', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dalam bertransaksi bisnis, sering dijumpai situasi dimana adanya satu atau sejumlah pihak yang terlibat dalam transaksi bisnis memiliki klaim atau kepentingan atas sejumlah dana, baik sebagai jaminan pembayaran transaksi atau sebagai agunan transaksi bisnisnya. &nbsp;Bank Muamalat Indonesia menghadirkan Jasa Layanan Escrow dimana Bank Muamalat Indonesia bertindak sebagai agen yang ditunjuk untuk mengelola, memantau, dan mengendalikan Escrow Account nasabah secara berkesinambungan. &nbsp;Rekening tersebut diperlakukan secara khusus dan dikelola sesuai dengan keinginan Anda yang dituangkan dalam Akad.</p>', '<p>Keuntungan yang Anda rasakan:</p>\r\n<p>1. Membantu Anda untuk memastikan agar pembayaran dilaksanakan tepat waktu.<br />2. Membantu Anda dalam mengelola dana dalam rekening <em>escrow</em> sesuai ketentuan dalam Akad.<br />3. Terjaminnya kepentingan Para Pihak</p>', '', '', 'jasa-layanan-escrow', 'jasa-layanan-escrow', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_311_depositojasa.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_311_depositojasa_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 04:44:01', '2016-03-20 07:27:55', 'admin', 'admin'),
(100, 2, 127, 99, 'Escrow Agency Services', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In the business transaction, often meet a situation where one or some parties involved in business transaction has claim or interest of fund, as well as transaction payment guarantee or other transaction guarantee.&nbsp; Bank Muamalat Indonesia provides Escrow Agency Services that act as agent appointed to manage, monitor, and control customer&rsquo;s Escrow Account continually.&nbsp; That account will treated specially dan managed according to Your desire that written on Akad.</p>', '<p>Benefits that You will get:</p>\r\n<p>1. Help you to ensure that the payment conducted on time.<br />2. Help you to manage fund in escrow account according on Akad.<br />3. Ensuring the interests of the parties.</p>', '', '', 'escrow-agency-services', 'escrow-agency-services', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_889_depositojasa.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_889_depositojasa_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 04:44:01', '2016-03-20 07:27:55', 'admin', 'admin'),
(101, 1, 127, 101, 'Corporate Debit Card', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kartu debit yang dimiliki oleh Nasabah korporasi dan memiliki fitur lengkap untuk bertransaksi seperti tarik tunai, transfer online antar rekening dan antar bank, beragam pembayaran seperti listrik, telepon, ponsel, dan sebagainya melalui ATM Muamalat. Corporate Debit Card merupakan fasilitas dari rekening Nasabah korporasi yang dapat diakses oleh banyak kartu dan dapat diberikan kepada mitra dari Nasabah korporasi untuk tujuan tertentu.</p>', '<p>Benefit yang akan Anda rasakan:</p>\r\n<p>1. Memudahkan perusahaan Anda untuk pengadaan kartu ATM tanpa harus berinvestasi pada pengadaan dan pengembangan ATM.<br />2. Meningkatkan channel transaksi bagi mitra perusahaan Anda.<br />3. Mitra perusahaan Anda tidak harus membuka rekening di Bank Muamalat Indonesia.</p>', '', '', 'corporate-debit-card', 'corporate-debit-card', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_314_depositodebit.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_314_depositodebit_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 04:52:56', '2016-03-20 07:28:57', 'admin', 'admin'),
(102, 2, 127, 101, 'Corporate Debit Card', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Debit card owned by corporate customer and has complete feature to do transaction such as cash withdrawal, online transfer other account or bank, many payment such as electricity, phone, mobile phone, etc via Muamalat ATM. &nbsp;Corporate Debit Card is a facilitation from corporate customer which can be accessed by many card and can be given to corporates customer&rsquo;s partner for certain purpose.</p>', '<p>Benefits that you will get:</p>\r\n<p>1. Ease Your corporate to make ATM card without invest in ATM making and development.<br />2. Increase transaction channel for Your corporate partner.<br />3. Your corporate partner do not have to open an account in Bank Muamalat Indonesia.</p>', '', '', 'corporate-debit-card', 'corporate-debit-card', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_381_depositodebit.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_381_depositodebit_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 04:52:56', '2016-03-20 07:28:57', 'admin', 'admin'),
(103, 1, 127, 103, 'Layanan Muamalat Cash Management', '<p>Merupakan fasilitas Internet Banking untuk nasabah Perusahaan yang memungkinkan nasabah memonitor maupun melakukan transaksi perbankan atas seluruh rekening yang berada di cabang Bank Muamalat di Indonesia secara <em>Realtime Online.</em></p>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Cakupan / Lingkup geografis yang luas</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Akses informasi keuangan yang cepat</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Kemudahan melakukan manajemen Kas</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Pelaporan dan rekonsiliasi data yang cepat dan akurat</li>\r\n</ol>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Berlaku untuk nasabah yang berbadan hukum (bukan perorangan)</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Memiliki rekening giro aktif di Bank Muamalat</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Mengisi dan menandatangani akad pembukaan serta syarat dan ketentuan Cash Management System Muamalat</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Biaya sesuai kebijakan Bank</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>Fitur </strong><strong>Muamalat Cash Management</strong><strong>:</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><em>Web-based</em> dengan tingkat keamanan yang baik</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Fasilitas yang <em>user</em> <em>friendly</em></li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Cakupan wilayah kerja yang luas</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Kemudahan dalam mengakses informasi yang diperoleh secara real time</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Manajemen dana yang lebih baik serta mengurangi <em>idle fund</em></li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Pilihan menu yang yang dapat disesuaikan dengan kebutuhan nasabah :</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Account Information (Balance Summary &amp; Detail History Transaction)</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Fund transfer (Single Transfer &amp; Multi Transfer)</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Bill payment including Zakat, Infaq &amp; Shadaqah</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Bulk transaction (Payroll, Bulk Transfer, Bulk Payment)</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Immediate Transaction</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Schedule Transaction</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Recurring Transaction</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\" value=\"7\">Pelaporan status keuangan serta rekonsiliasi data yang lebih cepat dan akurat</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\" value=\"8\">Investasi yang minimum</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Keamanan Muamalat Cash Management</strong><strong>:</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Koneksi akses langsung dan khusus secara <em>secure line</em> ke sistem Bank Muamalat</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Setiap nasabah memiliki User ID dan password sendiri yang unik</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">User Level, User ID dan password ditentukan sendiri oleh nasabah</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Transaksi menggunakan teknologi Encryption terkini</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><em>Test key generator</em> menggunakan Token yang telah terdaftar</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">User Level terdiri atas Maker, Checker dan Approver</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Helpdesk CMS</strong></p>\r\n<p>Layanan penanganan complain CMS dapat diakses melalui SalaMuamalat di No.Telp Khusus (021) 2949 3333.&nbsp; Waktu Layanan untuk penanganan complain adalah&nbsp; Senin-Jum&rsquo;at,&nbsp; pukul 08.00 -17.00 WIB,&nbsp; atau Email kami di: helpdesk.cms@muamalatbank.com.</p>', 'layanan-muamalat-cash-management', 'layanan-muamalat-cash-management', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_149_depositocash.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_149_depositocash_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 04:59:52', '2016-03-20 07:30:52', 'admin', 'admin');
INSERT INTO `list_produk_service` (`id`, `idlanguage`, `idpages`, `sister`, `title`, `description`, `benefit`, `syarat_pembukaan`, `fitur_umum`, `link`, `link_ori`, `submenu`, `parent`, `pic`, `pic_home`, `pic2`, `thumb`, `datestart`, `dateend`, `posisi`, `hapus`, `draft`, `cretime`, `modtime`, `creby`, `modby`) VALUES
(104, 2, 127, 103, 'Muamalat Cash Management', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Is Internet Banking &nbsp;facility for corporate customer which enable customer to monitor or do banking transaction in real time online for all account in Bank Muamalat.</p>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Broad geography coverage</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Fast financial information access</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Easiness to manage cash</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Fast and accurate data reporting and reconciliation</li>\r\n</ol>', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Terms &amp; Charge of Muamalat Cash Management:</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Incorporated customer</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Have an active current account in Bank Muamalat</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Complete and sign on the Opening Akad and the Term &amp; Condition of Muamalat Cash Management</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Charge based upon Bank&rsquo;s policy</li>\r\n</ol>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Web-based with high security level</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">User friendly facility</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Broad working area</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Easiness to access information in real time</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Better fund management and decrease idle fund</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Menu options that can be customized based on Customer&rsquo;s needs:</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Account information (Balance Summary &amp; Detail History Transaction)</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Fund Transfer (Single Transfer &amp; Multi Transfer)</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Bill payment including Zakat, Infaq &amp; Shadaqah</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Bulk transaction (Payroll, Bulk Transfer, Bulk Payment)</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Immediate Transaction</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Schedule Transaction</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Recurring Transaction</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li class=\"odd\" value=\"7\">Better and more accurate financial status reporting and data reconciliation</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\" value=\"8\">Minimum investation</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>The Security of Muamalat Cash Management</strong>:</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Direct and specific access connection with secure line to Bank Muamalat&rsquo;s system</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Every user have unique User IDs and password</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">User level, User ID, and password determined by the customer themselves</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">The transaction use the newest encryption technology</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Test key generator use registered token</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">User level consist of Maker, Checker, and Approver</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Helpdesk CMS</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>CMS Complaint Handling Helpdesk can be accessed through SalaMuamalat at (021) 29493333.&nbsp; Operating Hours is Monday &ndash; Friday, 08.00 &ndash; 17.00 WIB, or Email us: helpdesk.cms@muamalatbank.com</em></p>', 'muamalat-cash-management', 'muamalat-cash-management', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_801_depositocash.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_801_depositocash_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 04:59:52', '2016-03-20 07:30:52', 'admin', 'admin'),
(105, 1, 129, 105, 'Muamalat Remittance iB', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Adalah layanan pengiriman atau penerimaan uang valas dari atau kepada pihak ketiga kepada atau dari pemilik rekening Bank Muamalat Indonesia baik tunai maupun non tunai dalam denominasi valuta asing.</p>', '<ol class=\"teks\">\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><strong>Lengkap.</strong><br />Layanan Muamalat Remittance iB menyediakan berbagai skema pengiriman uang yang dapat diandalkan dengan harga yang bersahabat.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><strong>Handal.</strong><br />Layanan Muamalat Remittance iB didukung oleh SDM dan Teknologi Pendukung yang handal.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><strong>Nyaman.</strong><br />Melalui dukungan cabang dan jaringan kantor Bank Muamalat Indonesia, nasabah penerima kiriman uang melalui Layanan Muamalat Remittance iB dapat dengan leluasa menerima uang kirimannya.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><strong>Mudah.</strong><br />Kemudahan transaksi anda selalu menjadi perhatian kami.</li>\r\n</ol>', '', '<table border=\"0\" width=\"600\" cellpadding=\"2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<td bgcolor=\"#FFFFCC\" width=\"291\">\r\n<p class=\"green\"><em>Incoming Remittance</em>&nbsp;:</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td bgcolor=\"#FFFFCC\" width=\"295\">\r\n<p class=\"green\"><em>Outgoing Remittance</em>&nbsp;:</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"even\">\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<td><span class=\"style1\">Segmen</span><br />Semua nasabah Bank</td>\r\n<td><span class=\"style1\">Segmen</span><br />Semua nasabah Bank</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"even\">\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<td><span class=\"style1\">Jenis Nasabah</span><br />Perorangan maupun Institusional</td>\r\n<td><span class=\"style1\">Jenis Nasabah</span><br />Perorangan maupun Institusional</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"even\">\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<td valign=\"top\">\r\n<p><span class=\"style1\">Biaya</span>&nbsp;:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">Provisi</span><br />USD 0&nbsp;<br /><br />&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span class=\"style1\">Komunikasi</span><br />USD 0</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">Korespondensi</span><br />USD 0</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span class=\"style1\">Administrasi Bank</span><br />USD 5&nbsp;<br /><br />&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">Denda</span><br />USD 0</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p><span class=\"style1\">Counter Pengambilan Uang :&nbsp;</span><br />Bank dan semua jaringan Bank</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p><span class=\"style1\">Jenis mata uang asal yang dapat dilayani</span>&nbsp;:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">USD</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">EUR</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">SGD</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Aus Dollar</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">JPY</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">SAR</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">MYR</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><span class=\"style1\">Biaya</span>&nbsp;:<br />&nbsp;\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">Provisi</span><br />- Sumber dana : valas yang distransfer : 0.125% (min. USD 15 max. USD 150)<br />- Sumber dana : Rupiah/Beda valas : free</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span class=\"style1\">Komunikasi</span><br />Rp. 100.000,-</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">Korespondensi</span><br />USD 0</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span class=\"style1\">Kiriman</span><br />Pay in full amount /Our :<br />- USD : USD 25<br />- Non USD : USD 30&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">Denda</span><br />USD 0</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p><span class=\"style1\">Counter Pengambilan Uang :&nbsp;</span><br />Bank dan semua jaringan Bank</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p><span class=\"style1\">Jenis mata uang asal yang dapat dilayani</span>&nbsp;:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">USD</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">EUR</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">SGD</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Aus Dollar</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">JPY</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">SAR</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">MYR</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h4>Layanan produk Muamalat Remittance:</h4>\r\n<ol class=\"teks\">\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Outward Remittance</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Inward Remittance</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Kas Kilat Muamalat</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"teks\">Bank Muamalat siap memberikan solusi terbaik dan layanan prima untuk transaksi Remittance anda.<br />Informasi Lebih Lanjut:&nbsp;Hubungi kami di 021-2511414 ext. 393/558/657 untuk keterangan lebih lanjut.</p>\r\n<p class=\"teks\">Atau kunjungi cabang-cabang terdekat kami untuk memperoleh layanan produk-produk Muamalat Remittance.</p>', 'muamalat-remittance-ib', 'muamalat-remittance-ib', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_211_international-banking-mua.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_211_international-banking-mua_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 05:07:08', '2016-03-20 07:34:17', 'admin', 'admin'),
(106, 2, 129, 105, 'Remittance Muamalat iB', '<p>Is a service delivery or receipt of money from the foreign exchange or to any third party to or from the account holder of Bank Muamalat Indonesia both cash and non-cash foreign currency-denominated.</p>', '<ol class=\"teks\">\r\n<li class=\"odd\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Complete.</strong><br />IB Muamalat Remittance Services provides a variety of schemes that remittances reliable with a friendly price.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Reliable.</strong><br />IB Muamalat Remittance Services supported by Human Resources and Technology Supporting reliable.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Comfortable.</strong><br />Through the support and network of branch offices of Bank Muamalat Indonesia, the customer receiving remittances through Muamalat Remittance Service iB can freely receive remittances.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Easy.</strong><br />Ease your transaction has always been our concern.</li>\r\n</ol>', '', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table border=\"0\" width=\"600\" cellpadding=\"2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<td bgcolor=\"#FFFFCC\" width=\"291\">\r\n<p class=\"green\"><em>Incoming Remittance</em>&nbsp;:</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td bgcolor=\"#FFFFCC\" width=\"295\">\r\n<p class=\"green\"><em>Outgoing Remittance</em>&nbsp;:</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"even\">\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<td><span class=\"style1\">Segmen</span><br />Semua nasabah Bank</td>\r\n<td><span class=\"style1\">Segmen</span><br />Semua nasabah Bank</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"even\">\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<td><span class=\"style1\">Jenis Nasabah</span><br />Perorangan maupun Institusional</td>\r\n<td><span class=\"style1\">Jenis Nasabah</span><br />Perorangan maupun Institusional</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"even\">\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<td valign=\"top\">\r\n<p><span class=\"style1\">Biaya</span>&nbsp;:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">Provisi</span><br />USD 0&nbsp;<br /><br />&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span class=\"style1\">Komunikasi</span><br />USD 0</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">Korespondensi</span><br />USD 0</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span class=\"style1\">Administrasi Bank</span><br />USD 5&nbsp;<br /><br />&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">Denda</span><br />USD 0</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p><span class=\"style1\">Counter Pengambilan Uang :&nbsp;</span><br />Bank dan semua jaringan Bank</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p><span class=\"style1\">Jenis mata uang asal yang dapat dilayani</span>&nbsp;:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">USD</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">EUR</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">SGD</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Aus Dollar</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">JPY</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">SAR</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">MYR</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><span class=\"style1\">Biaya</span>&nbsp;:\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">Provisi</span><br />- Sumber dana : valas yang distransfer : 0.125% (min. USD 15 max. USD 150)<br />- Sumber dana : Rupiah/Beda valas : free</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span class=\"style1\">Komunikasi</span><br />Rp. 100.000,-</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">Korespondensi</span><br />USD 0</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span class=\"style1\">Kiriman</span><br />Pay in full amount /Our :<br />- USD : USD 25<br />- Non USD : USD 30&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">Denda</span><br />USD 0</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p><span class=\"style1\">Counter Pengambilan Uang :&nbsp;</span><br />Bank dan semua jaringan Bank</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p><span class=\"style1\">Jenis mata uang asal yang dapat dilayani</span>&nbsp;:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">USD</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">EUR</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">SGD</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Aus Dollar</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">JPY</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">SAR</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">MYR</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h4>Remittance services Muamalat products:</h4>\r\n<ol class=\"teks\">\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Outward Remittance</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Inward Remittance</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Quick Cash Muamalat</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"teks\">Bank Muamalat is ready to provide the best solutions and service excellence to your remittance transaction.<br />More Information:&nbsp;Contact us at 021-2511414 ext. 393/558/657 for more information.</p>\r\n<p class=\"teks\">Or visit our nearest branch to obtain services products Muamalat Remittance.</p>', 'remittance-muamalat-ib', 'remittance-muamalat-ib', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_745_international-banking-mua.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_745_international-banking-mua_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 05:07:08', '2016-03-20 07:34:17', 'admin', 'admin'),
(107, 1, 129, 107, 'Remittance BMI - MayBank  (Bank Muamalat Indonesia - MayBank)', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Adalah kiriman uang bagi TKI di Malaysia ke Indonesia melalui seluruh counter MayBank dan penerima kiriman dapat mengambil dana secara cash di seluruh cabang Bank Muamalat Indonesia.</p>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">Nyaman</span>, pengiriman uang dapat mengirimkan uangnya melalui seluruh counter MayBank di Malaysia (394 cabang) dan dapat menerima uang kiriman dalam bentuk cash di seluruh cabang BMI dengan menunjukkan identitas diri dan nomor referensi.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span class=\"style1\">Aman</span>, dana kiriman anda akan dikirimkan secara aman dan real time.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">Handal</span>, Layanan Kas KILAT-BMI MayBank didukung oleh SDM, Teknologi Pendukung yang handal</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span class=\"style1\">Mudah</span>, kemudahan proses transaksi baik bagi pengirim maupun penerima.</li>\r\n</ol>', '', '<p><strong>Via MayBank Money Express/MME :</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">RM 10</span>&nbsp;*), untuk layanan kiriman menggunakan MME, kepada penerima lain dan diterima dalam bentuk <em>cash</em>.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>*) Ada bulan-bulan gratis biaya kiriman, sesuai dengan program kerjasama antara BMI dan Maybank.</p>', 'remittance-bmi-maybank-bank-muamalat-indonesia-maybank', 'remittance-bmi-maybank-bank-muamalat-indonesia-maybank', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_615_international-bankingmay.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_615_international-bankingmay_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 05:13:40', '2016-03-20 07:35:54', 'admin', 'admin'),
(108, 2, 129, 107, 'Remittance BMI - MayBank  (Bank Muamalat Indonesia - MayBank)', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Are remittances for migrant workers in Malaysia to Indonesia through the entire counter MayBank and receiving shipments can take the funds in cash at all branches of Bank Muamalat Indonesia.</p>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">Comfortable</span>, remittances can send money through the entire counter MayBank in Malaysia (394 branches) and can receive remittances in cash at all branches of BMI by showing identification and reference number.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span class=\"style1\">Safe</span>, fund your shipment will be sent securely and in real time.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">Reliable</span>, Quick Cash Service-BMI MayBank supported by the SDM, reliable Supporting Technology</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span class=\"style1\">Easy</span>, easy transaction process for both the sender and the receiver.</li>\r\n</ol>', '', '<p><strong>Via MayBank Money Express/MME :</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">RM 10</span>&nbsp;*), for service delivery using the MME, the other recipients and received in cash.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>*) Some months free shipping, in accordance with the program of cooperation between BMI and Maybank.</p>', 'remittance-bmi-maybank-bank-muamalat-indonesia-maybank', 'remittance-bmi-maybank-bank-muamalat-indonesia-maybank', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_508_international-bankingmay.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_508_international-bankingmay_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 05:13:40', '2016-03-20 07:35:54', 'admin', 'admin'),
(109, 1, 129, 109, 'BMI - BMMB (Bank Muamalat Indonesia - Bank Muamalat Malaysia Berhad)', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">BMI - BMMB (Bank Muamalat Indonesia - Bank Muamalat Malaysia Berhad) adalah kiriman uang bagi TKI di Malaysia ke Indonesia melalui seluruh counter Bank Muamalat Malaysia Berhad kepada Nasabah Bank Muamalat Indonesia.</p>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"style1\">Nyaman</span>, pengiriman uang dapat mengirimkan uangnya melalui seluruh counter BMMB di Malaysia (55 cabang) dan penerima dapat menerima uang kiriman diseluruh cabang BMI.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"style1\">Aman</span>, dana kiriman anda akan dikirimkan secara aman dan real time.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"style1\">Handal</span>, Layanan Kas KILAT-BMMB didukung oleh SDM dan Teknologi Pendukung yang handal</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"style1\">Mudah</span>, kemudahan proses transaksi baik bagi pengirim maupun penerima.</li>\r\n</ol>', '', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"style1\">RM 1</span>, untuk layanan kiriman/setor ke rekening sendiri di Bank Muamalat Indonesia (pengirim dan penerima adalah ia sendiri dan nasabah BMI).</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"style1\">RM 5</span>, untuk layanan kiriman kepada penerima lain yang merupakan nasabah BMI.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"style1\">RM 10 *)</span>, untuk layanan kiriman menggunakan mesin EDC, baik kepada rekening sendiri atau kepada penerima lain yang merupakan nasabah BMI.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">*) dalam proses konfirmasi dengan BMMB</p>', 'bmi-bmmb-bank-muamalat-indonesia-bank-muamalat-malaysia-berhad', 'bmi-bmmb-bank-muamalat-indonesia-bank-muamalat-malaysia-berhad', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_223_international-bankingbmmb.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_223_international-bankingbmmb_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 05:23:21', '2016-03-20 07:37:20', 'admin', 'admin'),
(110, 2, 129, 109, 'BMI - BMMB (Bank Muamalat Indonesia - Bank Muamalat Malaysia Berhad)', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">BMI - BMMB (Bank Muamalat Indonesia - Bank Muamalat Malaysia Berhad) are remittances for migrant workers in Malaysia to Indonesia through the entire counter of Bank Muamalat Malaysia Berhad Bank Muamalat Indonesia to the Customer.</p>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">Comfortable</span>, remittances can send money through the entire counter BMMB in Malaysia (55 branches) and the receiver can receive remittances in all branches of BMI.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span class=\"style1\">Safe</span>, fund your shipment will be sent securely and in real time.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">Reliable</span>, Quick Cash Service-BMMB supported by Human Resources and Technology Supporting reliable</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span class=\"style1\">Easy</span>, easy transaction process for both the sender and the receiver.</li>\r\n</ol>', '', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">RM 1</span>, for a consignment service / deposited into his own account in Bank Muamalat Indonesia (sender and receiver are his own and customer BMI).</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span class=\"style1\">RM 5</span>, for service delivery to other recipients who are customers of BMI.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">RM 10 *)</span>, for service delivery using EDC, both to their own accounts or to other recipients who are customers of BMI.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>*) In the confirmation process with BMMB</p>', 'bmi-bmmb-bank-muamalat-indonesia-bank-muamalat-malaysia-berhad', 'bmi-bmmb-bank-muamalat-indonesia-bank-muamalat-malaysia-berhad', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_417_international-bankingbmmb.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_417_international-bankingbmmb_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 05:23:21', '2016-03-20 07:37:20', 'admin', 'admin'),
(111, 1, 129, 111, 'Remittance BMI - NCB (Bank Muamalat Indonesia - National Commercial Bank)', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Remittance BMI - NCB (Bank Muamalat Indonesia - National Commercial Bank) adalah kiriman uang bagi TKI di Arab Saudi ke Indonesia melalui seluruh counter PayQuick maupun fasilitas ATM National Commercial Bank kepada Nasabah Bank Muamalat Indonesia maupun Bank lain.</p>', '<ol class=\"teks\">\r\n<li class=\"odd\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nyaman</strong>, pengiriman uang dapat mengirimkan uangnya melalui seluruh counter PayQuick dan fasilitas ATM National Commercial Bank.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Aman</strong>, fitur layanan remittance kami melayani anda walaupun anda belum menjadi nasabah Bank Muamalat Indonesia, melalui fasilitas layanan Shar-e pick up *).</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Handal</strong>, Layanan Kas KILAT-BMI NCB didukung oleh SDM, Teknologi dan infrastruktur pendukung yang handal</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Mudah</strong>, kemudahan proses transaksi baik bagi pengirim maupun penerima.</li>\r\n</ol>', '', '<ol class=\"teks\">\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><strong>SAR 20</strong>, untuk semua jenis layanan kiriman baik kepada penerima di Bank Muamalat Indonesia ataupun Bank lain.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><em>*) Shar-e pick up adalah layanan kiriman uang khusus bagi mereka yang belum memiliki nomor rekening Bank Muamalat.</em></p>', 'remittance-bmi-ncb-bank-muamalat-indonesia-national-commercial-bank', 'remittance-bmi-ncb-bank-muamalat-indonesia-national-commercial-bank', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_113_international-bankingncb.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_113_international-bankingncb_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 05:26:44', '2016-03-20 07:38:50', 'admin', 'admin'),
(112, 2, 129, 111, 'Remittance BMI - NCB (Bank Muamalat Indonesia - National Commercial Bank)', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Are remittances for migrant workers in Saudi Arabia to Indonesia through the entire counter or ATM PayQuick National Commercial Bank to Bank Customers Bank Muamalat Indonesia and others.</p>', '<ol class=\"teks\">\r\n<li class=\"odd\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Comfortable</strong>, remittances can send money through the entire counter PayQuick and National Commercial Bank ATM facilities.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Aman</strong>, features our remittance services to serve you even if you are not a customer of Bank Muamalat Indonesia, through the facilities of Shar-e services pick up *).</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Reliable</strong>, Quick Cash Service-BMI NCB supported by HR, technology and reliable support infrastructure</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Easy</strong>, easy transaction process for both the sender and the receiver.</li>\r\n</ol>', '', '<ol class=\"teks\">\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><strong>SAR 20</strong>, for all kinds of good service delivery to recipients in Bank Muamalat Indonesia or another.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><em>*) Shar-e pick up is a special remittance service for those who do not have an account number Bank Muamalat.</em></p>', 'remittance-bmi-ncb-bank-muamalat-indonesia-national-commercial-bank', 'remittance-bmi-ncb-bank-muamalat-indonesia-national-commercial-bank', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_622_international-bankingncb.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_622_international-bankingncb_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 05:26:44', '2016-03-20 07:38:50', 'admin', 'admin'),
(113, 1, 129, 113, 'Tabungan Nusantara', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Adalah tabungan syariah yang dikelola dengan akad berbagi hasil dengan tambahan keuntungan kemudahan layanan remittance, sehingga selain menabung anda juga mudah melakukan transaksi Remittance.</p>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">Bebas Biaya Administrasi</span>.&nbsp;<br />Tabungan Nusantara merupakan tabungan yang bebas biaya administrasi (untuk saldo rata-rata tertentu) karena khusus diperuntukkan bagi nasabah perorangan dengan tujuan menabung selama bekerja di Malaysia.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span class=\"style1\">Murah.</span>&nbsp;<br />Gratis biaya penarikan tunai dicounter Bank di Indonesia. Nasabah juga diringankan oleh nominal pembukaan dan saldo minimum yang rendah.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">Sederhana.</span>&nbsp;<br />Tabungan Nusantara menyediakan ragam fasilitas dan ketentuan yang sangat cocok bagi nasabah yang membutuhkan layanan dan transaksi sederhana, seperti setoran, penarikan, transfer/remittance dengan tujuan penerimaan di Indonesia.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span class=\"style1\">Nyaman.</span>&nbsp;<br />Fasilitas tarik tunai di jaringan ATM yang luas baik di Indonesia dan Malaysia.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">Menguntungkan.</span><br />Adanya bagi hasil dan bebas biaya administrasi memungkinkan dana yang mengendap dapat terus bertambah secara halal.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span class=\"style1\">Tanpa Pajak.</span><br />Tidak kena pajak atas pendapatan bagi hasil yang diterima nasabah.</li>\r\n</ol>', '', '<h4>Biaya :</h4>\r\n<table class=\"no-border\" border=\"0\" width=\"472\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<td width=\"20\">1.</td>\r\n<td width=\"219\">Akad Mudharabah</td>\r\n<td width=\"13\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td width=\"194\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"even\">\r\n<td>2.</td>\r\n<td>Biaya paket</td>\r\n<td>:</td>\r\n<td>RM 10</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<td>3.</td>\r\n<td>Setoran awal</td>\r\n<td>:</td>\r\n<td>Rp. 20.000,-</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"even\">\r\n<td>4.</td>\r\n<td>Minimal setoran berikutnya</td>\r\n<td>:</td>\r\n<td>Rp. 10.000,-</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<td>5.</td>\r\n<td>Saldo minimum</td>\r\n<td>:</td>\r\n<td>Rp. 20.000,-</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"even\">\r\n<td>6.</td>\r\n<td>Nisbah bagi hasil</td>\r\n<td>:</td>\r\n<td>10% (nasabah) : 90% (bank)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<td>7.</td>\r\n<td>Biaya-biaya</td>\r\n<td>:</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"even\">\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td colspan=\"3\">\r\n<p>Administrasi<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- Saldo rata-rata harian &lt; Rp. 1.000.000,- = Rp. 1.000,-<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- Saldo rata-rata harian &gt;= Rp. 1.000.000,- = Rp. 0,-</p>\r\n<p>Penggantian kartu = RM 8</p>\r\n<p>Penarikan via counter<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- Malaysia : Gratis<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- Indonesia : Rp. 2.000,-</p>\r\n<p>Penarikan via non counter dan cek saldo<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- ATM Muamalat : Gratis<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- ATM BCA/Prima : Sesuai tarif penyedia layanan<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- ATM Bankad (Malaysia) : Sesuai tarif penyedia layanan</p>\r\n<p>Penutupan : Gratis&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'tabungan-nusantara', 'tabungan-nusantara', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_93_tabungannusantara.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_93_tabungannusantara_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 05:30:17', '2016-03-20 07:40:02', 'admin', 'admin'),
(114, 2, 129, 113, 'Nusantara Saving', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sharia is managed savings contract to share the results with the added advantage ease remittance services, so in addition to saving money you are also easy remittance transactions.</p>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">Free Shipping Administration.</span>.&nbsp;<br />Nusantara savings is savings administration fee (to a certain average balance) as specifically designed for individual customers with the goal of saving money while working in Malaysia.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span class=\"style1\">Cheap.</span>.&nbsp;<br />Free cash withdrawal fee dicounter Bank in Indonesia. The Customer is also alleviated by the opening par and low minimum balances.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">Simple.</span>.&nbsp;<br />Archipelago provides a range of savings and provision of facilities which is perfect for customers who need services and simple transactions, such as deposits, withdrawals, transfer / remittance receipts destination in Indonesia.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span class=\"style1\">Comfortable.</span>.&nbsp;<br />Cash withdrawal facility on extensive ATM network in both Indonesia and Malaysia.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><span class=\"style1\">Profitable.</span>.&nbsp;<br />Lack of shared revenue and administration fee allows funds to settle the growing halal.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><span class=\"style1\">Without taxes.</span>.&nbsp;<br />Not subject to tax on the income received by the customer results.</li>\r\n</ol>', '', '<h4>Cost :</h4>\r\n<table class=\"no-border\" border=\"0\" width=\"472\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<td width=\"20\">1.</td>\r\n<td width=\"219\">Mudaraba contract</td>\r\n<td width=\"13\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td width=\"194\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"even\">\r\n<td>2.</td>\r\n<td>Cost of package</td>\r\n<td>:</td>\r\n<td>RM 10</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<td>3.</td>\r\n<td>Initial deposit</td>\r\n<td>:</td>\r\n<td>Rp. 20.000,-</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"even\">\r\n<td>4.</td>\r\n<td>Minimal deposit next</td>\r\n<td>:</td>\r\n<td>Rp. 10.000,-</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<td>5.</td>\r\n<td>Minimum Balance</td>\r\n<td>:</td>\r\n<td>Rp. 20.000,-</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"even\">\r\n<td>6.</td>\r\n<td>Profit sharing ratio</td>\r\n<td>:</td>\r\n<td>10% (customer): 90% (bank)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"odd\">\r\n<td>7.</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;Costs</td>\r\n<td>:</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"even\">\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td colspan=\"3\">\r\n<p>Administration<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; - Average daily balance &nbsp; &nbsp; - Average daily balance&gt; = Rp. 1.000.000, - = Rp. 0, -<br />Replacement cards = RM 8<br />Withdrawal via counter<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; - Malaysia: Free<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; - Indonesia: Rp. 2,000, -<br />Withdrawal via non counter and checks and balances<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; - ATM Muamalat: Free<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; - ATM BCA / Prima: As service providers rates<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; - ATM Bankad (Malaysia): As service providers rates<br />Closure: Free</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'nusantara-saving', 'nusantara-saving', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_979_tabungannusantara.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_979_tabungannusantara_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 05:30:17', '2016-03-20 07:40:02', 'admin', 'admin'),
(115, 1, 131, 115, 'Bank Garansi', '<p class=\"par1\"><strong>Bank Garansi</strong> (atau disingkat <strong>BG</strong>) adalah Jaminan Pembayaran yang diberikan oleh Bank atas permintaan Nasabahnya, kepada pihak penerima jaminan dalam hal Nasabah yang dijamin tidak memenuhi kewajibannya kepada pihak penerima jaminan.</p>\r\n<p class=\"par1\">BG merupakan fasilitas non dana (&nbsp;<em>Non Funded Facility&nbsp;</em>) yang diberikan Bank berdasarkan akad Kafalah bil Ujrah. Bank akan menerbitkan BG sejumlah nilai tertentu yang dipersyaratkan oleh pihak penerima jaminan yang merupakan klien/mitra bisnis/&nbsp;<em>counter part&nbsp;</em>dari Nasabah Bank untuk kepentingan transaksi / proyek tertentu yang akan dijalankan oleh Nasabah Bank.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>Penggunaan dan macam Bank Garansi</h4>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Diberikan kepada pemborong atau kontraktor untuk mengerjakan proyek</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Diberikan untuk menjamin pembayaran (dapat berupa&nbsp;<em>Standby L/C&nbsp;</em>)</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Sedangkan <strong>Bank Garansi</strong> yang umum digunakan dalam rangka proyek, untuk mendukung usaha konstruksi, adalah:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Bid Bond&nbsp;</em>/&nbsp;<em>Tender Bond&nbsp;</em>atau jaminan saat mengikuti tender</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Advance Payment Bond&nbsp;</em>atau jaminan uang muka</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Performance Bond&nbsp;</em>atau jaminan pelaksanaan selama masa konstruksi</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>Produk <strong>Bank Garansi</strong> yang bisa kami sediakan adalah :</p>\r\n<ol start=\"1\" type=\"1\">\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><strong><em>Bid Bond&nbsp;</em></strong><strong>/&nbsp;<em>Tender Bond</em></strong><em>,&nbsp;</em>diterbitkan untuk kebutuhan peserta tender guna mengikuti tender di dalam negeri</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><strong><em>Advance Payment Bond</em></strong>atau jaminan uang muka, diterbitkan untuk kebutuhan penerima pekerjaan guna menjamin pelaksanaan pekerjaan setelah diterimanya pembayaran uang muka dari pemilik proyek</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\"><strong><em>Performance Bond</em></strong><em>, d</em>iterbitkan untuk kebutuhan penerima pekerjaan guna menjamin selesainya proyek yang diterima atau untuk kepentingan pembeli guna menjamin pembayaran atas barang yang telah diterima</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\"><strong><em>Retention Bon</em></strong><em>,&nbsp;</em>diterbitkan untuk kebutuhan pemohon guna menjamin pemeliharaan proyek yang telah diselesaikan</li>\r\n</ol>', '', '', '', 'bank-garansi', 'bank-garansi', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_240_bank_garansi.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_240_bank_garansi_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 05:40:25', '2016-03-20 08:16:47', 'admin', 'admin'),
(116, 2, 131, 115, 'Bank Guarantee', '<p class=\"par1\">Bank Guarantee (BG for short) is a payment guarantee provided by the Bank at the request of its Customers, to any of the insured in the event the Customer is guaranteed not to meet its obligations to the insured party.</p>\r\n<p class=\"par1\">BG is a non-fund facilities (Non Funded Facility) of the Bank based on contract Kafalah Ujrah bil. BG Bank will publish a certain number of values ??required by the receiving party assurance that a client / business partner / customer counter part of the Bank for the benefit of the transaction / specific projects that will be executed by the Customer Bank.</p>\r\n<h4>And wide use of Bank Guarantee</h4>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Given to the contractor or contractors for the project</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Given to ensure payment (either Standby L / C)</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>While the Bank Guarantees are commonly used in the context of the project, to support the construction business, are:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Bid Bond / Tender Bond or warranty as to bid</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Advance Payment Bond or deposit guarantee</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Performance Bond or performance bonds during construction</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>Bank Guarantee products we can provide are:</p>\r\n<ol start=\"1\" type=\"1\">\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Bid Bond / Tender Bond, issued to the bidders need to participate in the tender in the country</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Advance Payment Bond or advance payment guarantee, issued to the needs of the work in order to ensure the execution of the work after receipt of advance payment from the project owner</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Performance Bond, issued to the needs of the work in order to ensure the completion of projects that received or for the benefit of the buyer to secure payment for goods that have been received</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Retention Bond, published for the needs of the applicant to ensure the maintenance projects that have been completed</li>\r\n</ol>', '', '', '', 'bank-guarantee', 'bank-guarantee', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_254_bank_garansi.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_254_bank_garansi_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 05:40:25', '2016-03-20 08:16:47', 'admin', 'admin'),
(117, 1, 131, 117, 'Trade Finance - Ekspor', '<h4>Layanan yang diberikan:</h4>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Advising L/C dan perubahannya.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Transfer L/C.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Konfirmasi L/C.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Negosiasi Wesel Ekspor.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Collection dokumen L/C.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Collection dokumen non L/C.</li>\r\n</ol>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Melalui jaringan koresponden Bank Muamalat yang luas, Nasabah dapat menerima L/C dari bank manapun di seluruh dunia.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Layanan advisory dan konsultasi dalam mempersiapkan dokumen ekspor.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Untuk negosiasi wesel ekspor Bank Muamalat dapat memberikan layanan secara cepat dan tepat, sepanjang persyaratan telah terpenuhi.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Secara syariah, produk/Layanan untuk eksporter didasarkan pada Akad Al-Wakalah, Al Qard, maupun Al Hiwalah</li>\r\n</ol>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Eksportir adalah nasabah Bank Muamalat.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Menyerahkan surat permohonan pengambil-alihan wesel ekspor.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Menyerahkan asli dokumen ekspor.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Telah dilakukan risk asessment terhadap transaksi yang akan dilakukan.</li>\r\n</ol>', '', 'trade-finance-ekspor', 'trade-finance-ekspor', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_125_ekspor.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_125_ekspor_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 05:44:47', '2016-03-20 08:26:48', 'admin', 'admin'),
(118, 2, 131, 117, 'Trade Finance - Ekspor', '<h4>Services provided:</h4>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Advising L/C and changes.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Transfer L/C.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Confirmation of L/C.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Export Bills negotiation.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Collection documents L/C.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Collection documents the non L/C.</li>\r\n</ol>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Through a network of correspondent Bank Muamalat broad, Customer may receive L/C from any bank in the world.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Advisory and consultancy services in preparing export documents.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">To export bill negotiation Bank Muamalat to provide services quickly and accurately, all the requirements have been met.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">In sharia, products/services to exporters based on Al-Wakalah Agreement, Al Qard, and Al Hiwalah.</li>\r\n</ol>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Exporters are customers of Bank Muamalat.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Submit its application for expropriation export bills.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Submit original export documents.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Have done risk assessment and the transaction to be carried out.</li>\r\n</ol>', '', 'trade-finance-ekspor', 'trade-finance-ekspor', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_755_ekspor.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_755_ekspor_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 05:44:47', '2016-03-20 08:26:48', 'admin', 'admin'),
(119, 1, 131, 119, 'Trade Finance - Impor', '<h4>Layanan yang diberikan:</h4>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Issuing L/C.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Amendment L/C.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Realisasi L/C berupa penerimaan dan pemeriksaan dokumen serta penyelesaian pembayaran.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Inward Collection dokumen Impor non L/C.</li>\r\n</ol>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">L/C yang diterbitkan oleh Bank Muamalat dapat diterima oleh bank manapun diseluruh dunia.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Didukung oleh tenaga ahli dan berpengalaman dalam pemeriksaan dokumen impor.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Konsultasi dan advisory seputar impor.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Fasilitas Refinancing L/C dengan biaya dan pricing yang kompetitif.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Layanan cepat dan akurat.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Secara syariah, Produk/Layanan untuk impoter didasarkan pada akad Al-Wakalah, Al-Kafalah, Al-Qard, Al-Hiwalah, maupun Al-Murabahah.</li>\r\n</ol>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Importir adalah nasabah Bank Muamalat.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Mempunyai Angka Pengenal Impor.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Mengisi aplikasi permohonan pembukaan atau perubahan L/C.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Menyerahkan Marginal Deposit sesuai dengan ketentuan.</li>\r\n</ol>', '', 'trade-finance-impor', 'trade-finance-impor', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_32_impor.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_32_impor_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 05:49:42', '2016-03-20 08:27:13', 'admin', 'admin'),
(120, 2, 131, 119, 'Trade Finance - Import', '<h4>Services provided:</h4>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Issuing L/C.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Amendment L/C.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Realization of L/C in the form of acceptance and inspection of documents and payment settlement.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Inward Collection Import documents non L/ C.</li>\r\n</ol>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">L/C issued by Bank Muamalat can be received by any bank worldwide.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Powered by experts and experienced in the inspection of import documents.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Consulting and advisory about imports.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Refinancing Facility L/C at a cost and competitive pricing.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Service is fast and accurate.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">In sharia, Products/Services for impoter based on Al-Wakalah contract, Al-Kafalah, Al-Qard, Al-Hiwalah, and Al-Murabahah.</li>\r\n</ol>', '<ol>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Importer is a customer of Bank Muamalat.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Imports have identity numbers.</li>\r\n<li class=\"odd\">Fill out an application or amendment application for opening L/C.</li>\r\n<li class=\"even\">Submit Marginal Deposit in accordance with the provisions.</li>\r\n</ol>', '', 'trade-finance-import', 'trade-finance-import', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_200_impor.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_200_impor_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 05:49:42', '2016-03-20 08:27:13', 'admin', 'admin'),
(121, 1, 131, 121, 'Produk/Layanan Untuk Perdagangan Dalam Negri SKBDN (Surat Kredit Berdokumen Dalam Negeri)', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bank Muamalat menyediakan layanan untuk transaksi SKBDN atau lazim dikenal dengan nama L/C dalam negeri untuk mendukung kelancaran bisnis anda.<br /><br />Pada dasarnya produk dan layanan yang disediakan untuk Eksporter dan Importer, dapat juga digunakan untuk mendukung perdagangan dalam negri. Yang membedakana hanya penggunaan yurisdiksi hukum, dimana dalam transaksi ekspor/impor menggunakan standar internasional yang diatur dalam UCP DC&nbsp;<em>(Uniform Custom Practice on Documentary Collection)</em>, sementara untuk transaksi dalam negri, mengikuti ketentuan dari Bank Indonesia.&nbsp;<br /><br />Produk dan layanan SKBDN mempunyai karakteristik yang sama dengan produk dan layanan pada transaksi ekspor impor. Persyaratan dan ketentuan untuk SKBDN merujuk pada syarat dan ketentuan transaksi ekspor impor.</p>', '', '', '', 'produk-layanan-untuk-perdagangan-dalam-negri-skbdn-surat-kredit-berdokumen-dalam-negeri', 'produk-layanan-untuk-perdagangan-dalam-negri-skbdn-surat-kredit-berdokumen-dalam-negeri', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_812_skbdn.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_812_skbdn_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 05:55:29', '2016-03-20 08:28:34', 'admin', 'admin'),
(122, 2, 131, 121, 'Product/Service For Trading In Foreign SKBDN (Domestic Letter of Credit)', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bank Muamalat provides services for transaction SKBDN or commonly known as the L / C in the country to support the smooth running of your business.<br /><br />Basically the products and services provided to exporters and importers, can also be used to support domestic trade. Which membedakana only use legal jurisdiction, where the transaction of export / import using international standards set out in DC UCP (Uniform Custom Practice on Documentary Collection), while for the transaction in the country, following the provisions of Bank Indonesia.&nbsp;<br /><br />SKBDN products and services have the same characteristics with the products and services on export import transactions. SKBDN terms and conditions refer to the terms and conditions of trade transactions.</p>', '', '', '', 'product-service-for-trading-in-foreign-skbdn-domestic-letter-of-credit', 'product-service-for-trading-in-foreign-skbdn-domestic-letter-of-credit', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_21_skbdn.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_21_skbdn_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 05:55:29', '2016-03-20 08:28:34', 'admin', 'admin'),
(123, 1, 131, 123, 'Letter of Credit', '<p class=\"par1\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Letter of Credit</strong>&nbsp;secara sederhana merupakan Pengambilalihan tanggung jawab pembayaran oleh pihak lain (dalam hal ini diambil alih oleh Bank) atas dasar permintaan pihak yang dijamin&nbsp;<strong>(Applicant/Pembeli/Nasabah Bank)</strong>&nbsp;untuk melakukan pembayaran kepada pihak penerima jaminan&nbsp;<strong>(Beneficiary/Penjual)</strong>&nbsp;berdasarkan syarat dan kondisi yang ditentukan dan disepakati.</p>\r\n<p class=\"par1\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sebagaimana BG, LC juga merupakan fasilitas non dana, dimana Bank dalam hal ini bertindak sebagai wakil dari Pembeli - menggunakan akad Wakalah bil Ujrah - untuk pengurusan dokumen, sementara untuk pembayaran penyelesaian transaksinya dapat menggunakan dana Nasabah sendiri maupun menggunakan fasilitas pembiayaan dari Bank dengan akad seperti yang telah di uraikan sebelumnya (Piutang Murabahah, Piutang Istishna, Mudharabah atau Musyarakah).</p>', '', '', '', 'letter-of-credit', 'letter-of-credit', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_968_letter_of_credit.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_968_letter_of_credit_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 06:12:14', '2016-03-20 08:28:53', 'admin', 'admin'),
(124, 2, 131, 123, 'Letter of Credit', '<p class=\"par1\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Letter of Credit is simply a responsibility Takeover payment by another party (in this case taken over by the Bank) at the request of the secured party (Applicant / Buyer / Customer Bank) to make payments to the insured party (Beneficiary / Seller) by the terms and conditions set forth and agreed upon.</p>\r\n<p class=\"par1\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">As BG, LC is also a non-fund facilities, which the Bank in this case acting as a representative of the buyer - using Wakalah bil Ujrah contract - for the processing of documents, while the settlement of payment transactions to be able to use its own funds and use the Customer\'s facility with the Bank\'s financing of such contract which has been described previously (Murabaha receivables, receivables Istishna, Mudaraba or Musharaka).</p>', '', '', '', 'letter-of-credit', 'letter-of-credit', 0, 0, 'list_produk_service_175_letter_of_credit.jpg', '', '', 'list_produk_service_175_letter_of_credit_small.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '2016-03-20 06:12:14', '2016-03-20 08:28:53', 'admin', 'admin');
