(9, 1, 5, 74, 9, 'PROUDLY PAPUA', 1, '', '<p><img src=\"https://eternaleaf.com/assets/backend/js/tinymce/plugins/image/uploads/proudly_1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"427\" height=\"128\" /></p>\r\n<p>Papua is located at the most eastern part of Indonesian Archipelago. With the majestic Jayawijaya Mountains including lush green tropical forests, Papua is a home to a rich, dense, and lively ecosystem. Those what inspires us to give the best nature can offer, specifically for you.</p>', '1background_20160825064146_papua-section.png', NULL, '1image20160825064146_peta-papua.png', '', 5, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, '', '', '', 0, 0, '2016-08-25 06:41:46', '2017-05-02 13:54:24', 'admin', 'admin'),
(10, 2, 5, 74, 9, 'WHY RED?', 0, '', '<p>Terletak di timur Indonesia, Papua dikelilingi oleh Pegunungan Jayawijaya dan hutan hujan tropis yang kaya. Papua dikenal dengan keanekaragaman hayati yang tinggi, salah satunya adalah Buah Merah.</p>', '2background_20161016213224_whyred.png', NULL, '2image20161016213224_whyred1.png', '', 5, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, '', '', '', 0, 0, '2016-08-25 06:41:46', '2017-05-02 13:54:24', 'admin', 'admin'),
(11, 1, 5, 74, 11, 'EMBRACING CULTURE', 0, '', '<p>The Dani People, live in Baliem Valley of Papua. This valley is placed strategically with its fertile soil and rich forest. The local native tribe believes that they must live eloquently and peacefully side by side with nature, makes farming and raising cattle as their primary source of living.</p>', '1background_20160825064318_embracing.png', NULL, '', '', 6, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 2, '#FFFFFF', 'col-xs-6', 'col-xs-6', 0, 0, '2016-08-25 06:43:20', '2016-11-05 00:09:58', 'admin', 'admin'),
(12, 2, 5, 74, 11, 'EMBRACING CULTURE', 0, '', '<p>Suku Asli Papua yaitu Suku Dani, tinggal di Lembah Baliem. Lembah ini terletak di daerah subur dengan sumber daya alam yang kaya. Suku Dani hidup selaras dengan alam, bertani dan beternak adalah cara mereka untuk mendapatkan sumber makanan.</p>', '2background_20161025184827_1background_20160825064318_embracing_(1).png', NULL, '', '', 6, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 2, '#FFFFFF', 'col-xs-6', 'col-xs-6', 0, 0, '2016-08-25 06:43:20', '2016-11-05 00:09:58', 'admin', 'admin'),
(13, 1, 5, 74, 13, 'BUAH MERAH PAPUA', 0, '', '<p>Its bright red color indicates the fruit is rich in all nature&rsquo;s good. Only found in Papua, this fruit also provides Omega 3, Omega 6, Selenium, Alpha Tocopherol and Antioxidant for your skin needs.</p>\r\n<p>We have invested our passion and dedication in a research about this magnificent fruit. After 16 years of hard work and anticipation, our scientific research has come to its conclusion, and we proudly declare that Buah Merah Papua:</p>\r\n<p>1.Has the highest antioxidant compared to all fruit.</p>\r\n<p>2.Contains the most complete nutritional composition.</p>\r\n<p>3.High in Beta-carotene, Beta-Chriptoxhatin and Tocopherol or Vitamin E.</p>\r\n<p>4.Contains essential Omega 3, 6, 9 and Essential Micro-Mineral Selenium.</p>', '1background_20160825064439_papua-fruit.png', NULL, '', '', 7, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 3, '#FFFFFF', 'col-xs-6', 'col-xs-6', 0, 0, '2016-08-25 06:44:39', '2016-10-26 11:30:47', 'admin', 'admin'),
(14, 2, 5, 74, 13, 'BUAH MERAH PAPUA', 0, '', '<p>Kami melakukan riset dengan dedikasi tinggi. Setelah kerja keras dan semangat yang dicurahkan selama 16 tahun, kesimpulan dari riset saintifik kami adalah:</p>\r\n<p>1.Buah Merah memiliki antioksidan paling tinggi dibanding buah lainnya.</p>\r\n<p>2.Mengandung komposisi nutrisi kompleks yang berguna bagi kesehatan kulit.</p>\r\n<p>3.Tinggi Betakaroten, Beta-Chriptoxhatin dan Tocopherol atau Vitamin E.</p>\r\n<p>4.Mengandung Omega 3, 6, 9 dan Selenium.</p>', '2background_20161026113047_whyred-buah_merah.png', NULL, '', '', 7, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 3, '#FFFFFF', 'col-xs-6', 'col-xs-6', 0, 0, '2016-08-25 06:44:39', '2016-10-26 11:30:47', 'admin', 'admin'),
(15, 1, 5, 74, 15, 'WHY PANDANUS CONOIDEUS', 0, '', '<p>Knowing the potential of the fruit, prior to establishing Eternaleaf we have invested 16 years of our time researching this fruit. Based on our research backed by scientific and lab analysis we can simply conclude and declare that \"Buah Merah\":</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;No. 1 highest Anti-Oxidant in the fruit kingdom</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Contains the most complete nutritional composition</li>\r\n<li>High in Beta-carotene, &beta;-Chriptoxhantin and Tocopherol / Vitamin E</li>\r\n<li>Contain essential fatty acid Omega 3, 6, 9 &nbsp; Essential Micro-mineral Selenium</li>\r\n</ol>', '1background_20160825064601_whybuahmerah.png', NULL, '1image20160825064603_grafik.png', '', 7, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 4, '#FFFFFF', 'col-xs-6', 'col-xs-6', 0, 1, '2016-08-25 06:46:03', '2016-09-10 10:08:11', 'admin', 'admin'),
