(17, 1, 5, 74, 17, 'Eternaleaf', 1, '', '<p style=\"color: #000;\"><img src=\"https://eternaleaf.com/assets/backend/js/tinymce/plugins/image/uploads/Logo-Eternaleaf-Big.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"40%\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000;\">Papua, Indonesia, despite being one of the richest region in the world in terms of resources and bio-diversities, its people are yet still one of the poorest in Indonesia even in the world.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000;\">Eternaleaf was established in March 1st, 2015 to identify potential Papua heritage and wisdom and commercializing it with the primary objective of using part of its profit to assist in the development of Papua region and its people. We want something that\'s is Proudly Papua.</p>', '1background_20160825064703_wanita.png', NULL, '', '', 7, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 6, '#000000', 'col-xs-6', 'col-xs-6', 0, 0, '2016-08-25 06:47:05', '2017-05-03 13:31:17', 'admin', 'admin'),
(18, 2, 5, 74, 17, 'Eternaleaf', 0, '', '<p style=\"color: #000;\"><img src=\"https://eternaleaf.com/assets/backend/js/tinymce/plugins/image/uploads/Logo-Eternaleaf-Big.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"40%\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000;\">Eternaleaf mengawali jejaknya bersama buah merah papua sejak bulan Maret 2015. Kami sadar bahwa Papua memiliki potensi alam dan kebudayaan yang amat besar. Dua hal inilah yang ingin kami sebarkan ke seluruh dunia. Kami berusaha untuk memasarkan produk Papua untuk membangun Papua. Kami berkomitmen untuk menyuarakan \"Proudly Papua\".</p>', '2background_20161026112532_whyred-eternaleaf.png', NULL, '', '', 7, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 6, '#000000', 'col-xs-6', 'col-xs-6', 0, 0, '2016-08-25 06:47:05', '2017-05-03 13:31:17', 'admin', 'admin'),
